      <title>比特币跌回 65,000 美元以下，9 月份收盘下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/bitcoin-drops-back-below-65-000-to-finish-september-on-a-down-note</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币以下跌结束了 9 月份最大的一次反弹，跌回 65,000 美元以下，削弱了人们对进入历史上加密货币回报最好的月份的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/bitcoin-drops-back-below-65-000-to-finish-september-on-a-down-note</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 19:08:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Olive Garden 所有者 Darden 出售债券以资助 Chuy 的收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/olive-garden-owner-darden-to-sell-bonds-to-fund-chuy-s-purchase</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Darden Restaurants Inc. 是 Olive Garden 和 LongHorn Steakhouse 等连锁餐厅的所有者，该公司以 7.5 亿美元进军美国高端餐厅市场，为其计划收购德州-墨西哥连锁餐厅 Chuy’s 提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/olive-garden-owner-darden-to-sell-bonds-to-fund-chuy-s-purchase</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 18:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
